  "detailed_description": "\"When you are flying in the sky of a vast world, swimming in the sea, defeating enemies,<br>or searching for your roots, what do you really know...?\"<br>Faye/Sleepwalker is a vast world of exploration and hectic battles. <br>Enjoy a high speed action game and the development of an interesting story in an open world.<br><br>Battles are divided into two modes, a normal mode with easy control of actions, <br>and the sleepwalk mode with high-speed actions and warp attacks,<br>allowing you to experience new sensations of actions.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480520/extras/97332ca813aea4fc7f8d4a8f6d360b68.poster.avif?t=1611500433\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480520/extras/97332ca813aea4fc7f8d4a8f6d360b68.webm?t=1611500433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480520/extras/97332ca813aea4fc7f8d4a8f6d360b68.mp4?t=1611500433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Combo</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480520/extras/ebba18afd44a91c6c263d3baa930674b.poster.avif?t=1611500433\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480520/extras/ebba18afd44a91c6c263d3baa930674b.webm?t=1611500433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480520/extras/ebba18afd44a91c6c263d3baa930674b.mp4?t=1611500433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Battle</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/st